# Keep BOTH submission PDFs tracked so reviewers can grab them straight off
# GitHub without rebuilding from source. main_anonymous.pdf is for the RRPR
# blind review; main_arxiv.pdf is the author-credited version for arXiv.
!main_anonymous.pdf
!main_arxiv.pdf
